# Normalize all text files to LF on commit AND force LF in the working tree on
# checkout. Without `eol=lf`, Windows users with the default `core.autocrlf=true`
# get CRLF in the working tree and tools that compare against the index (biome
# format, run-bundle hash comparisons) silently flag every text file as drifted.
# `eol=lf` makes the working tree match the index on every platform.
* text=auto eol=lf
